---
import Layout from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Layout title="Workshop Replay — Footwork & Foundation | Thee Rainers">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta name="description" content="90-minute recorded workshop. Footwork, stance, punching mechanics, defensive structure. Watch on demand. $79." />
  </Fragment>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-white px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 pt-32 md:pt-40 pb-20 border-b border-[#0A0A0A]/8">
    <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto w-full">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[3fr_2fr] gap-16 md:gap-24 items-start">

        <div>
          <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-8">On Demand · Full Recording</p>
          <h1 class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A] uppercase tracking-tighter text-5xl md:text-6xl leading-[0.85] mb-8">
            The Workshop<br/>Replay
          </h1>
          <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/50 text-base leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-[440px]">
            90 minutes. Footwork, stance, punch mechanics, defensive structure — and a live Q&A session at the end. The same session that went live in May. Watch it now, on your schedule.
          </p>

          <div class="border border-[#0A0A0A]/8 p-8 mb-10 max-w-[440px]">
            <div class="flex flex-col divide-y divide-[#0A0A0A]/8">
              <div class="flex justify-between py-3">
                <span class="text-[#0A0A0A]/40 text-sm">Format</span>
                <span class="text-[#0A0A0A]/70 text-sm font-bold">Full recording · watch anytime</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between py-3">
                <span class="text-[#0A0A0A]/40 text-sm">Length</span>
                <span class="text-[#0A0A0A]/70 text-sm font-bold">90 minutes</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between py-3">
                <span class="text-[#0A0A0A]/40 text-sm">Access</span>
                <span class="text-[#0A0A0A]/70 text-sm font-bold">Instant · 7-day access link</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between py-3">
                <span class="text-[#0A0A0A]/40 text-sm">Price</span>
                <span class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A] text-xl">$79</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 max-w-[360px]">
            <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/6oUaEX7hp6Xk3LIdww6J20p" target="_blank"
              class="blue-btn inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold border-2 border-[#0057FF] text-[#0057FF] bg-transparent px-10 py-4 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#0057FF] hover:text-white">
              Get the Replay — $79 →
            </a>
            <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/20 text-xs tracking-wide text-center">Instant access. Watch immediately after checkout.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: curriculum -->
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-[2px]">
          <div class="bg-[#F6F6F6] border border-[#0A0A0A]/8 p-6">
            <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">01</p>
            <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/70 text-sm font-bold mb-1">Footwork & Balance</p>
            <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/35 text-xs leading-relaxed">The errors draining your stamina and making you stiff. Ground contact, weight distribution, pivot mechanics.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#F6F6F6] border border-[#0A0A0A]/8 p-6">
            <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">02</p>
            <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/70 text-sm font-bold mb-1">Athletic Stance</p>
            <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/35 text-xs leading-relaxed">Build your custom stance — the platform where you attack and defend simultaneously.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#F6F6F6] border border-[#0A0A0A]/8 p-6">
            <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">03</p>
            <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/70 text-sm font-bold mb-1">Punch Mechanics</p>
            <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/35 text-xs leading-relaxed">Stop pushing and start snapping. Power from the kinetic chain — not the shoulder.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#F6F6F6] border border-[#0A0A0A]/8 p-6">
            <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">04</p>
            <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/70 text-sm font-bold mb-1">Defensive Structure</p>
            <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/35 text-xs leading-relaxed">Boxing with purpose. Defence built into offence — not added on after.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#F6F6F6] border border-[#0A0A0A]/8 p-6">
            <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">05</p>
            <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/70 text-sm font-bold mb-1">Live Q&A Recording</p>
            <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/35 text-xs leading-relaxed">Real questions, real answers. Specific mechanical problems diagnosed in real time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTIMONIAL -->
  <section class="bg-white px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-20 border-b border-[#0A0A0A]/8">
    <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_3fr] gap-16 items-center">

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start">
        <div class="border border-[#0A0A0A]/8 overflow-hidden w-full max-w-[280px]">
          <div class="relative w-full" style="padding-bottom: 177.78%;">
            <iframe
              src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VCj0Dgfoako"
              title="Giancarlo — 5 months"
              allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
              allowfullscreen
              class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full"
            ></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mt-4">Giancarlo · 5 Months</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">The result of this work</p>
        <p class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A]/55 uppercase tracking-tighter text-2xl md:text-3xl leading-[0.9] mb-6">
          "My footwork makes sense. I could see openings instead of just swinging."
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/40 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-[400px]">
          Giancarlo went through Private Architecture for 5 months before a scheduled fight. What you see in this short started with the same mechanics taught in this workshop.
        </p>
        <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/6oUaEX7hp6Xk3LIdww6J20p" target="_blank"
          class="blue-btn inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold border-2 border-[#0057FF] text-[#0057FF] bg-transparent px-10 py-4 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#0057FF] hover:text-white">
          Get the Replay — $47 →
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- UPSELL: Live workshop -->
  <section class="bg-white px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-20 border-b border-[#0A0A0A]/8">
    <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto w-full flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-end justify-between gap-12">
      <div class="max-w-[540px]">
        <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">After the replay</p>
        <h2 class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A] uppercase tracking-tighter text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-[0.85] mb-4">
          Want real-time<br/>correction?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">The replay gives you the framework. The Calibration Workshop on June 27 gives you live diagnosis — camera on, your movement, real corrections in real time.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/workshop"
        class="blue-btn inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold border-2 border-[#0057FF] text-[#0057FF] bg-transparent px-10 py-4 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#0057FF] hover:text-white shrink-0">
        Reserve June 27 Seat — $197 →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SCRIPTURE -->
  <section class="bg-[#0A0A0A] px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto">
      <p class="font-black uppercase tracking-tighter leading-[0.88] mb-4 text-white/50 text-2xl md:text-3xl">
        "I do not run aimlessly. I do not fight like a boxer beating the air."
      </p>
      <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">1 Corinthians 9:26</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
